description: Soul Train - We Are The Soul [2010] DVD5 26 participations of various artists on the TV show Soul Train. Released in 2010 and only in Japan. Soul Train is an American music-dance television program which aired in syndication from October 2, 1971 to March 27, 2006. In its 35-year history, the show primarily featured performances by R&B, soul, dance/pop and hip hop artists, although funk, jazz, disco and gospel artists also appeared. The series was created by Don Cornelius, who also served as its first host and executive producer.
